import InputGroup from 'react-bootstrap/InputGroup';
import Form from 'react-bootstrap/Form';
import { Row,Col, Container } from 'react-bootstrap';

function Clients() {
  return (
    <>
    <Container>
      <Row>
        <Col lg={7}>
        <Form.Control size="lg" type="text" placeholder="Name" id="CompanyName" />
        </Col>
      </Row>
    <Row className='my-5'>
      <Col lg={6}>
        <Row className='mb-2'>
          <Col>
            <Form.Label htmlFor="Company Adresse">Company Adresse:</Form.Label>
            </Col>
          <Col>
            <Form.Control size="sm" type="text" placeholder="Small text"  id="Company Adresse" />
            </Col>
            </Row>
        <Row className='mb-2'>
          <Col lg={{ span: 6, offset: 6 }}>
            <Form.Control size="sm" type="text" placeholder="Small text" id="Company Adresse" />
            </Col>
            </Row>
        <Row className='mb-2'>
          <Col lg={{ span: 6, offset: 6 }}>
          <Row >
            <Col lg={4}>
              <Form.Control size="sm" type="text" placeholder="Small text" id="Company Adresse" />
              </Col>
            <Col lg={4}>
              <Form.Control size="sm" type="text" placeholder="Small text" id="Company Adresse" />
              </Col>
            <Col lg={4}>
              <Form.Control size="sm" type="text" placeholder="Small text" id="Company Adresse" />
              </Col>
              </Row>
            </Col>
          <Col lg={{ span: 6, offset: 6 }}>
            <Form.Control size="sm" type="text" placeholder="Small text" />
            </Col>
          </Row>
        <Row>
          <Col><Form.Label htmlFor="CompanyName">GST treatment:</Form.Label></Col>
          <Col><Form.Control size="sm" type="text" placeholder="Small text" /></Col>
        </Row>
        <Row>
          <Col><Form.Label htmlFor="CompanyName">VAT:</Form.Label></Col>
          <Col><Form.Control size="sm" type="text" placeholder="Small text" /></Col>
        </Row> 
      </Col>
      <Col lg={4}>
        <Row>
          <Col><Form.Label htmlFor="Phone">Phone:</Form.Label></Col>
          <Col><Form.Control size="sm" type="text" placeholder="2029311" id="Phone" /></Col>
        </Row>
        <Row>
          <Col><Form.Label htmlFor="Mobile">Mobile:</Form.Label></Col>
          <Col><Form.Control size="sm" type="text" placeholder="2029311" id="Mobile" /></Col>
        </Row>
        <Row>
          <Col><Form.Label htmlFor="Email">Email:</Form.Label></Col>
          <Col><Form.Control size="sm" type="text" placeholder="2029311" id="Email" /></Col>
        </Row>
        <Row>
          <Col><Form.Label htmlFor="Website Link">Website Link:</Form.Label></Col>
          <Col><Form.Control size="sm" type="text" placeholder="2029311" id="Website Link" /></Col>
        </Row>
        <Row>
          <Col><Form.Label htmlFor="Tags">Tags:</Form.Label></Col>
          <Col><Form.Control size="sm" type="text" placeholder="2029311" id="Tags" /></Col>
        </Row>
        
        
        
        
        
        
        
        
        
        

      </Col>
      </Row>
      </Container>

    </>
  );
}

export default Clients;
